<p>I recently started a twinkie bard and have him up to 19. When I am getting new instrument skills as I level I just go sit in Felwithe and pop whatever instrument needs skillups and hit a song that uses that instrument and in no time its maxed. Another little quick thing I do is pop on a fishbone earring and jump in the water in Felwithe and sing while swimming into a wall. In no time you will have you swimming and singing/instrument maxed. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sat Sep 25 14:05:54 2004 by Zwingli</span></i> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sat Oct&nbsp;&nbsp;9 17:14:00 2004 by Zwingli</span></i></p>
