<p><blockquote><b class="sm">Quote:</b><hr size="1" />Also higher dexterity = less missed notes<hr size="1" /></blockquote> <br /> <br />I just answered another thread about this... dex effects your missed notes VERY little. Charisma has a much larger impact on missed notes. On top of that, if a lull fails, the games does a check against your charisma to see if it's a critical resist or not (if it's a critical resist, the mob aggros, if not, he just stands there and you get to try again). Now to your questions: <br /> <br />1. Dex DOES help with skillups, just not missed notes. <br /> <br />2. Just start the song and let it roll.</p>
