<p>INT effects how quickly you learn skills.&nbsp;&nbsp;They will go up faster if your INT is high, although if you are going to just stand around AFK and play, it won't really matter how fast it goes up. <br /> <br />As long as you don't play an annoying song in Bazaar, it's fine if you play while you're in trader mode.  For example, the mid-20's fear song does not spam a message if it hits them, so that's good to increase brass.  For wind instruments, use the enduring breath song.  For string, use the level six healing spell (it's been months since I played regularly, I can't even remember the names of the spells).  For percussing, Selo's won't annoy anyone.</p>
